            <div class="section">
                <h2>Rotation</h2>
                <ol class="rotation-steps">
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Activate Armored Hide</strong> -- Keep this active permanently. The thorns damage and DR it provides are essential for the build's core loop. Without Armored Hide, Payback bursts lose most of their damage amplification.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Soar into dense packs</strong> -- Use Soar to dive into the center of enemy groups. The invulnerability frames during Soar let you position safely. Aim to land surrounded by as many enemies as possible.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Cast Payback immediately</strong> -- Activate Payback the moment you land. This opens your counter-attack window. For the next few seconds, every hit you take charges up retaliation damage.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Cast Concussive Stomp</strong> -- Stun all nearby enemies while Payback is active. This freezes them in place so they keep hitting you during the counter-attack window. The Attack Speed bonus also amplifies your retaliation hit rate.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Absorb hits during Payback window</strong> -- Stand still and let enemies hit you. Each hit charges Payback and triggers thorns damage. With Ocelot's Eye, blocked hits also trigger automatic counter-attacks. The more hits you take, the bigger the burst.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Unleash Payback burst</strong> -- When Payback expires or you manually detonate, all absorbed damage explodes in a massive retaliation burst. This single hit can delete entire packs if you absorbed enough damage.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Use The Protector during dangerous phases</strong> -- Pop ultimate when facing high burst damage or elite packs. The Unstoppable and defensive bonuses let you safely absorb massive incoming damage, then unleash enormous Payback bursts.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Escape with Soar when cooldowns are down</strong> -- After bursting, your defensive cooldowns are down. Use Soar to reposition out of danger until Payback and Armored Hide are back up. Avoid lingering in packs without active defenses.</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2>Gameplay Tips</h2>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>You must intentionally take damage.</strong>
                    <p>This build's entire identity revolves around absorbing hits to charge Payback bursts. If you play too defensively and avoid damage, you deal no damage. Embrace the chaos -- dive into packs, absorb hits, then explode.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Timing is everything.</strong>
                    <p>Payback windows are short. You need to absorb as many hits as possible before the window expires. Concussive Stomp's stun is critical -- it keeps enemies attacking you instead of scattering. Without CC, enemies may move away before you finish charging.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Positioning is life or death.</strong>
                    <p>Always position in the center of packs before casting Payback. If you're on the edge, enemies hit you from one side only. In the center, they surround you and hit from all angles, maximizing hits absorbed and Payback damage.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Ocelot's Eye is your defensive and offensive MVP.</strong>
                    <p>The Block Chance it provides triggers automatic counter-attacks via the Counterattack skill. Each blocked hit becomes instant retaliation damage layered on top of Payback bursts. The more Block Chance you stack, the more free damage you generate.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Manage cooldowns carefully.</strong>
                    <p>Your survivability windows are tied to skill cooldowns. Payback and Armored Hide must be active before diving into packs. If they're on cooldown, wait or reposition. Fighting without active defenses is suicide in high-tier content.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>This build is slower than Evade builds.</strong>
                    <p>Payback Spiritborn trades speed for power. You can't spam Evade infinitely like Quill Volley or The Seeker builds. Accept the slower pace -- your reward is massive burst damage that deletes entire screens when timed correctly.</p>
